ChordChartAreaAdapter
public abstract class BaseChordChartAreaAdapter
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
implements java.io.Serializable

The base class for the chord chart area table model that holds chord chart objects. Extends the AbstractTableModel and implements the Serializable interface.
